column2: This task consists of performing the hello world task that Google Summer of Code students do. It is a necessary step to be able to build RTEMS itself and perform some of the other GCI tasks. instructions at http://www.rtems.org/wiki/index.php/GoogleCodeInProjects#Run_and_Modify_GSOC_Hello_World_Procedure. This task can only be performed once per GCI student.
